title: The 13 Ghosts of Scooby Doo The Complete Series DVD RIP
description:
Format: MP4


All 13 Episodes of season 1



Multi Audio


Multi Subtitles



Doo, Daphne, Shaggy and Scrappy Doo, a team of "ghostbusters" who had to catch 13 ghosts which Shaggy and Scooby released when they were tricked to open the "Chest of Demons" by 2 ghosts. The ghosts are causing disasters all around the world and they have to put them back in the chest before things get even worse.

The gang is joined by the great Vincent Van Ghoul and a boy named Flim-Flam. They are constantly annoyed by 2 ghosts called Weerd and Bogel. These 2 ghosts will do almost everything to prevent the gang from catching the ghosts. Fortunately, these ghosts are a bit dumb!
